videos.description: Morris Udeze gets a steal and passes ahead to a wide-open Dexter Dennis who botches the easy dunk attempt to the disappointment of the home crowd.

videos.description: Wichita State's Tyson Etienne gets a steal and passes to Jamarius Burton, who spins in traffic and banks it home through contact for the and-1 score.
